    "type": "spell",
    "data": {
        "description": {
            "value": "<p>You use your mind to manipulate unattended objects in the area, temporarily animating them to attack. The objects hover in the air, then hurl themselves at nearby creatures in a chaotic flurry of debris. This assault deals [[/r 2d10 #bludgeoning]]&nbsp; bludgeoning damage (basic Reflex save) to each creature in the area. On subsequent rounds, you can @Compendium[pf2e.actionspf2e.3f5DMFu8fPiqHpRg]{Sustain the Spell}, dealing [[/r 1d10#bludgeoning]] bludgeoning damage (basic Reflex save) to each creature in the area.</p>\n<hr>\n<p><strong>Heightened (+2)</strong> The initial damage increases by [[/r 2d10]] and the subsequent damage increases by [[/r 1d10]].</p>",
